events.name: GDG Patna Launch Event Meetup
events.description:
Hey Patna, GDG Patna (Google Developer Group) is launching soon.
We welcome you at the LAUNCH EVENT of GDG Patna which will be held on December 31, 2019.

Our motto behind organising the meetup is to give a brief introduction about "GDG Patna".
The agenda of this event is :
1. Introduction to GDG Patna.
2. A brief description about our plans for GDG Patna and the motto behind it.
3. Feedback & Suggestion from other members.
4. A final wrap-up of the event.

Those who are interested to join us at the event will have to fill the form available on the link mentioned below.
https://forms.gle/ewe6CE8yLWAVA9L89

Invitation will be sent to limited people on their email with venue and other details.

events.name: Exploring the world of web
events.description:
GDG Patna & Khabai Tech co-presesents THE WORLD OF WEB.
Agenda of the event
1. Introduction to the Web
2. Kick start with HTML5.
3. Styling the web with CSS3.
4. Make your portfolio - Mini Hackathon.
5. Share with your friends.
6. Exciting prizes.

Note : This is a hands-on training. Laptop is compulsory for your participation.
